  "text": "Treatment is surgical. Previously orchidectomy was the option. In the recent literature there is strong recommendation of tumor enucleation as the most appropriate treatment for testicular benign lesions. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] We have opted for testis sparing surgery and our patient showed a recurrence free follow up of more than three years (to this date).",
